            <lg xml:id="TK858">
<l>ikaliṟ ketircāyta lākka mataṉai</l>
<l>mikalūkki ṉūkkamāṅ kēṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Shrinking back from hatred will yield wealth indulging in its increase will hasten ruin.</l>
